OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,FThe head of the Criminal Cases Review
OL,8,FCommission (CCRC) has resigned, saying
OL,9,Fthat she was made a scapegoat over the
OL,10,FAndrew Malkinson case.
OL,12,FMr Malkinson spent 17 years behind
OL,13,Fbars for a rape in Salford he did not
OL,14,Fcommit and labelled CCRC chairwoman
OL,15,FHelen Pitcher's comments as a
OL,16,F"shameless" attempt to "portray
OL,17,Fherself as the victim", adding that he
OL,18,Fknows what it "truly is like" to be a
OL,19,Fscapegoat.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@KO]xD@XOUyD@VO]zD@OOUzD@]O]
