OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,FHe called for a complete overhaul of
OL,8,Fthe CCRC, claiming the body
OL,9,F"obstructed my fight for justice", and
OL,10,Frepeated demands for Ms Pitcher to be
OL,11,Ffired and stripped of her OBE after a
OL,12,Freview was published in July 2024.
OL,14,FIt found that wrongly jailed Mr
OL,15,FMalkinson was failed by the CCRC and
OL,16,Fcould have been exonerated nearly a
OL,17,Fdecade earlier, prompting Justice
OL,18,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood to say Ms
OL,19,FPitcher was "unfit to fulfil her
OL,20,Fduties" and to seek her removal from
OL,21,Fthe post.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@aO]{D@MOU|D@GO]
