OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,FIn her resignation letter to the
OL,8,FJustice Secretary, Ms Pitcher said she
OL,9,Ffeels it is "unfair" she has been
OL,10,F"singled out" in receiving the level
OL,11,Fof scrutiny that she has over her part
OL,12,Fin the litany of failings in Mr
OL,13,FMalkinson's case.
OL,15,F"I understand the fury over this grave
OL,16,Fmiscarriage of justice and believe
OL,17,Fthat serious questions remain for
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Police and the
OL,19,FCrown Prosecution Service," she said.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@TO]rD@AOUrD@MO]wD@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
