OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,F"I note that the DPP and the Chief
OL,8,FConstable of the GMP have not been
OL,9,Fsubject of comparable criticism. It
OL,10,Ffeels unfair that I, who was fully
OL,11,Fsupportive of the reference to the
OL,12,FCourt of Appeal, have been singled out
OL,13,Fbut the others have not been the
OL,14,Fsubject of similar proceedings.
OL,16,F"I do feel I have been scapegoated for
OL,17,Fentirely legitimate operational
OL,18,Fdecisions that were not handled by any
OL,19,Fnon-executive CCRC chair before I
OL,20,Fjoined the organisation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
