OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,F"The original rejection of Mr
OL,8,FMalkinson's appeal was almost a decade
OL,9,Fbefore my time: on my watch, armed
OL,10,Fwith new DNA evidence which we
OL,11,Fcommissioned, we were able to resolve
OL,12,Fthe situation, and set Mr Malkinson
OL,13,Ffree."
OL,15,FThe 66-year-old also said in her
OL,16,Fletter: "A head had to roll, and I was
OL,17,Fchosen for that role."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@FO]xD@IOUyD@VO]
