OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,FFurther, Pitcher warned it "may prove
OL,8,Fextremely difficult" to find a new
OL,9,Fchair prepared to take on a role in
OL,10,Fwhich she says "they will be held
OL,11,Fpersonally responsible for historical
OL,12,Ffailures over which they will have had
OL,13,Fno say".
OL,15,F"This approach is reminiscent of the
OL,16,FConservative Business Secretary who
OL,17,Fsacked Henry Staunton as Chairman of
OL,18,Fthe Post Office because 'someone has
OL,19,Fto take the rap'," she continued.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@TO]rD@POUuD@GO]wD@AOU{D@RO]
