OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,F"Like me he joined that organisation
OL,8,Fto fix the failures that had already
OL,9,Foccurred. It is worthy of note that
OL,10,Fthe CCRC were instrumental in the
OL,11,Foverturning of Miscarriages of Justice
OL,12,Ffor the Sub-Postmasters."
OL,14,FMr Malkinson criticised Ms Pitcher
OL,15,Ffollowing her resignation.
OL,17,FIn a statement provided by legal
OL,18,Fcharity Appeal ` which supports Mr
OL,19,FMalkinson ` he said: "Helen Pitcher's
OL,20,Fattempt to portray herself as the
OL,21,Fvictim here is shameless.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@YO]{D@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
