OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,F"I know what it truly is like to be a
OL,8,Fscapegoat."
OL,10,FHe called for further resignations.
OL,12,F"I agree, however, that others need to
OL,13,Fbe held accountable," Mr Malkinson
OL,14,Fsaid. "The CCRC's senior leadership,
OL,15,Fstarting with the CEO, must also
OL,16,Fresign to pave the way for root-and-
OL,17,Fbranch reform.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@KO]tD@AOUuD@UO]vD@GOU
