OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,F"I am astonished that the outgoing
OL,8,Fchair claims that the CCRC was able to
OL,9,F'resolve the situation,' and set me
OL,10,Ffree. That work was done by my team at
OL,11,FAPPEAL, not the CCRC, who were
OL,12,Fconsidering rejecting my case for a
OL,13,Fthird time.
OL,15,F"Going forward, it is crucial that the
OL,16,FCCRC is led by people with the guts to
OL,17,Fchallenge miscarriages of justice,
OL,18,Feven if that means taking on forces
OL,19,Flike the police and judiciary."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@_O]
