OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,FMatt Foot, co-director of Appeal,
OL,8,Fcalled Ms Pitcher's resignation "a
OL,9,Freal victory".
OL,11,F"This is clearly the right decision
OL,12,Fand a real victory for those of us
OL,13,Fcampaigning for an effective
OL,14,Fmiscarriage of justice watchdog," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,26,@pD@aOUqD@MO]sD@AOUvD@aO]
