OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,F"Helen Pitcher proved herself an unfit
OL,8,Fleader when she shamelessly sought
OL,9,Fpraise for her organisation's
OL,10,Fcatastrophic mishandling of Andrew
OL,11,FMalkinson's case and then spent months
OL,12,Fdenying him an apology.
OL,14,F"The priority now must be to get in a
OL,15,Fnew chair and a fresh senior
OL,16,Fleadership team with experience of
OL,17,Ffighting injustice, who can restore
OL,18,Fpublic confidence in the CCRC.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
