OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,F"Miscarriage of justice survivors,
OL,8,Fcampaigners and lawyers should all be
OL,9,Fconsulted to make sure that the right
OL,10,Fpeople are selected."
OL,12,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid: "The Lord Chancellor established
OL,14,Fan independent panel to consider Helen
OL,15,FPitcher's role as chair of the CCRC.
OL,16,FWe welcome her resignation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@UO]uD@GOU
