OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson calls ex-head of
OL,4,Cmiscarriage of justice watchdog
OL,5,C'shameless'
OL,7,F"Given the importance of the CCRC's
OL,8,Fwork, we will appoint an interim chair
OL,9,Fas quickly as possible who will be
OL,10,Ftasked with conducting a full and
OL,11,Fthorough review of how the
OL,12,Forganisation operates."
OL,14,FA CCRC spokesperson said: "We welcome
OL,15,Fthe clarity given by Mrs Pitcher's
OL,16,Fdecision and look forward to working
OL,17,Fwith the interim chair to continue the
OL,18,Fimportant task of finding,
OL,19,Finvestigating and referring to the
OL,20,Fappeal courts possible miscarriages of
OL,21,Fjustice."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@WO]vD@[OU}D@IO]
